sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as modelmesh-controller
    participant ETCD as ETCD<br/>2379/TCP HTTP/gRPC
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Service as modelmesh-serving Service
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>8001/TCP gRPC
    participant Puller as Storage Puller<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 1: InferenceService Creation
        User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate request<br/>TLS 1.2+, K8s API cert
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validation response
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch notification<br/>ServiceAccount token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment, Service<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
        Controller->>ETCD: Initialize model metadata<br/>Optional TLS
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over Puller,S3: Flow 2: Model Loading from Storage
        Puller->>K8sAPI: Read storage-config Secret<br/>ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>Puller: S3 credentials
        Puller->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>AWS Signature V4
        S3-->>Puller: Model files
        Note over Puller,Runtime: Shared volume (filesystem)
        Puller-->>Runtime: Model available on shared volume
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 3: gRPC Inference Request
        Client->>Service: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>Optional app-level auth
        Service->>ModelMesh: Forward gRPC request<br/>No encryption
        ModelMesh->>ETCD: Lookup model metadata<br/>Optional TLS
        ETCD-->>ModelMesh: Model location
        ModelMesh->>Runtime: Execute inference<br/>UDS or 8001/TCP gRPC
        Runtime-->>ModelMesh: Prediction result
        ModelMesh-->>Service: gRPC response
        Service-->>Client: Inference result
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 4: REST Inference Request
        Client->>Service: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>8008/TCP HTTP<br/>Optional app-level auth
        Service->>RESTProxy: Forward HTTP request<br/>No encryption
        RESTProxy->>ModelMesh: Translate to gRPC<br/>8033/TCP
        ModelMesh->>Runtime: Execute inference<br/>UDS or 8001/TCP gRPC
        Runtime-->>ModelMesh: Prediction result
        ModelMesh-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
        RESTProxy-->>Service: HTTP response
        Service-->>Client: JSON result
    end

    rect rgb(245, 245, 245)
        Note over Client,Controller: Flow 5: Metrics Collection
        Client->>Controller: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token
        Controller-->>Client: Prometheus metrics
        Client->>Service: GET /metrics<br/>2112/TCP HTTP<br/>No auth
        Service-->>Client: Runtime metrics
    end
